      <arrangement id="aspace_a05262191f3d78345425cc98fde3dffd">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into three series. I. George Fountain Glass Plate and Photographic Negatives of World War I, 1919, 1978. II. Lantern Slides Related to Silent Film and Stereopticon, circa 1910s-1920s. III. Motion Picture Films, circa 1910s-1920s.</p>
